*</ept> event with an argument of <bpt id=\"p2\">[</bpt><bpt id=\"p3\">**</bpt>String.Empty<ept id=\"p3\">**</ept><ept id=\"p2\">](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/xaml/system.string.empty.aspx)</ept> or <bpt id=\"p4\">**</bpt>null<ept id=\"p4\">**</ept> indicates that all non-indexer properties on the object should be re-read.","pos":[8964,9206]},{"content":"You can raise the event to indicate that indexer properties on the object have changed by using an argument of \"Item<ph id=\"ph1\">\\[</ph><bpt id=\"p1\">*</bpt>indexer<ept id=\"p1\">*</ept><ph id=\"ph2\">\\]</ph>\" for specific indexers (where <bpt id=\"p2\">*</bpt>indexer<ept id=\"p2\">*</ept> is the index value), or a value of \"Item<ph id=\"ph3\">\\[\\]</ph>\" for all indexers.","pos":[9207,9440]},{"content":"A binding source can be treated either as a single object whose properties contain data, or as a collection of objects.","pos":[9442,9561]},{"content":"In C# and Visual Basic code, you can one-time bind to an object that implements <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt><bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>List(Of T)<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept><ept id=\"p1\">](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/xaml/6sh2ey19.aspx)</ept> to display a collection that does not change at run-time.","pos":[9562,9784]},{"content":"For an observable collection (observing when items are added to and removed from the collection), one-way bind to <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt><bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>ObservableCollection(Of T)<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept><ept id=\"p1\">](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/xaml/ms668604.aspx)</ept> instead.","pos":[9785,10008]},{"content":"In C++ code, you can bind to <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt><bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Vector<ph id=\"ph1\">&amp;lt;</ph>T<ph id=\"ph2\">&amp;gt;</ph><ept id=\"p2\">**</ept><ept id=\"p1\">](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/dn858385.aspx)</ept> for both observable and non-observable collections.","pos":[10009,10161]},{"content":"To bind to your own collection classes, use the guidance in the following table.","pos":[10162,10242]},{"content":"Scenario","pos":[10246,10254]},{"content":"C# and VB (CLR)","pos":[10312,10327]},{"content":"C++/CX","pos":[10732,10738]},{"content":"Bind to an object.","pos":[12145,12163]},{"content":"Can be any object.","pos":[12211,12229]},{"pos":[12632,12832],"content":"Object must have <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt><bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>BindableAttribute<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept><ept id=\"p1\">](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/Hh701872)</ept> or implement <bpt id=\"p3\">[</bpt><bpt id=\"p4\">**</bpt>ICustomPropertyProvider<ept id=\"p4\">**</ept><ept id=\"p3\">](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/BR209878)</ept>."},{"content":"Get property change updates from a bound object.","pos":[13137,13185]},{"pos":[13203,13381],"content":"Object must implement <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt><bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>System.ComponentModel. INotifyPropertyChanged<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept><ept id=\"p1\">](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/xaml/system.componentmodel.inotifypropertychanged.aspx)</ept>."},{"pos":[13680,13811],"content":"Object must implement <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt><bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Windows.UI.Xaml.Data. INotifyPropertyChanged<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept><ept id=\"p1\">](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/BR209899)</ept>."},{"content":"Bind to a collection.","pos":[14162,14183]},{"content":"List(Of T)","pos":[14231,14241]},{"content":"Platform::Collections::Vector<ph id=\"ph1\">&amp;lt;</ph>T","pos":[14681,14715]},{"content":"Get collection change updates from a bound collection.","pos":[15171,15225]},{"content":"ObservableCollection(Of T)","pos":[15240,15266]},{"content":"Platform::Collections::Vector<ph id=\"ph1\">&amp;lt;</ph>T","pos":[15670,15704]},{"content":"Implement a collection that supports binding.","pos":[16160,16205]},{"content":"Extend <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt><bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>List(Of T)<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept><ept id=\"p1\">](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps